# .NET Node Variant

.NET SDK image with Node.js support for full-stack development.

## Included Tools

- .NET SDK (version depends on tag)
- Node.js {{ .Versions.nodejs }}
- npm package manager

## Usage

```dockerfile
FROM __hive__/dotnet:8.0.100-node

# Build backend
RUN dotnet build -c Release

# Build frontend
RUN npm install && npm run build
```

## Versions

- Node.js: {{ .Versions.nodejs }}
